Author: beaglesarebest
Text: Last night I had a nightmare so real I woke up sweating and shaking. I dreamt that I stepped on the scale and had gained weight.

Author: PieldeSapo
Text: Yes I have bingeing nightmares where I eat and can't stop and I wake up extremely upset and disoriented and i always have a hard to tell if it actually happened or not in the beginning when I wake up.
